Package: PLMScoRe
Type: Package
Title: Derives PLM and other indices according to WASM rules
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Stephany Fulda
Maintainer: Stephany Fulda <stephany.fulda@gmail.com>
Description: Takes information about leg movements, sleep, arousal, and respiratory events
    as input and returns descriptive statistics/indices about leg movement activity including 
    intermovement interval plots. At the moment only REMLogic event txt files are the supported
    input. For more information see https://github.com/Steph-Fulda/PLMScoRe
